        "speaker": "Luke",
        "text": "I'd always assumed that it was just that we didn't have room in our [blank] for all that [blank].",
        "blanks": [
          { "answer": "memories" },
          { "answer": "stuff" }
        ],
        "translation": "我一直以为只是我们的记忆中没有空间容纳那些东西。"
