        "text": "However, getting the produce to places where it could be marketed was sometimes a problem, as the farmers did not have access to transport, and this resulted in large amounts of produce, especially vegetables, being [blank]. This problem was discussed with the [blank] and it was decided that in order to prevent food from being spoiled, the farmers needed to learn techniques for its preservation.",
