        "text": "They aren't really good enough to enter national band [blank] but they're [blank] in a regional one later in the term. Even if they don't win, and I don't expect them to, hopefully it'll be an [blank] for them to try and improve.",
        "blanks": [
          { "answer": "competitions" },
          { "answer": "competing" },
          { "answer": "incentive" }
        ],
        "translation": "他们还没有足够的能力进入全国乐队比赛，但是他们在这个学期后期会进入区域性比赛。即使他们没有获胜，我也没指望他们能获胜，只是希望这会激励他们努力并且进步。"
