        "speaker": "Joe",
        "text": "Can I tell you about a few people in the band who I'm finding it quite difficult to [blank]? I'm sure you'll have some ideas about what I can do.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "cope with" }],
        "translation": "我可以告诉你，我发现乐队里的一些人很难应付吗？我相信你会对于我能做什么提些建议。"
