        "text": "So as you might expect, she's found that the urban blackbirds [blank] quite [blank] - they're prepared to face up to a lot of [blank] that would frighten away their country [blank]. But there's one type of situation that does seem to frighten the urban blackbirds, and that's anything new - anything they haven't experienced before. And if you think about it, that's quite [blank] for a bird living in the city.",
