        "speaker": "Speaker",
        "text": "One particularly successful project last year was the Get Working Project. This was helping [blank] in the area get back to work. Our staff were able to help them improve their telephone skills, such as writing down messages and speaking with [blank] to [blank], which they had found quite difficult.",
