        "speaker": "Speaker",
        "text": "If you're interested in [blank], please go to the volunteering section of our website and complete the [blank]. We won't be providing any training for this but you'll be paired with an experienced volunteer if you've never done it before. By the way, don't forget to tell your manager about any volunteering activities you [blank] to do.",
