        "text": "I think having nutritional food labeling has been a good idea, don't you? I think it will change [blank] and stop mothers, in particular, buying the wrong things.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "people's behaviour" }],
        "translation": "我认为贴营养食品标签是个好主意，你说呢？我认为它将改变人们的行为，特别是阻止妈妈们买错东西。"
