        "text": "Yes, that'd be interesting, and raise all sorts of issues. Let's [blank] of possible things we could ask about, then work out some sort of [blank]. For instance, um, we could interview some of the staff, and find out whether the library has its own budget, or if that's controlled by the [blank].",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "make a list" }, { "answer": "structure" }, { "answer": "local council" }],
        "translation": "好主意，这个应该会很有趣。我们可以提出所有方面的问题。我们来做一个我们可能会问及的问题的列表吧，然后做一个合理的结构出来。比如，我们可以采访一些里面的员工，弄清楚这个图书馆是不是有自己的预算，还是由当地委员会负责。"
