        "text": "And what their policies are. I know they don't allow food, but I'd love to find out what types of [blank] they [blank] - there always seems to be a lot of talking, but never [blank]. I don't know if that's a policy or it just happens.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "noise" }, { "answer": "ban" }, { "answer": "music" }],
        "translation": "还有图书馆的政策。我知道他们是不允许带食物进去的，但是我更想知道他们禁止的噪音都有什么类型。那里总是有很多人交谈，但从不会允许播放音乐。我不知道这是明文规定还是事情本身如此。"
