        "text": "Ah, I've often wondered. Then there are things like how the library is affected by [blank]. I suppose there are rules about working hours, facilities for staff, and so on.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "employment laws" }],
        "translation": "啊，我也一直很好奇。然后，还有雇佣条款是如何影响到图书馆本身的。我觉得他们对于工作时间，员工使用的设施以及其他东西都应该有规定。"
