        "text": "The festival will be opened [blank] by the [blank]. He'll just speak for a few minutes, welcoming everyone to the festival. All the town councillors will be there, and of course lots of other people.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "officially" }, { "answer": "mayor" }],
        "translation": "节日将由市长正式宣布开幕。他会发表几分钟的讲话，欢迎大家来参与这个节日。所有的市议员都会出席，当然也还有很多别的人。"
