        "text": "Yeah. I've looked at the [blank] you've done for my story, 'The Forest', and I think they're brilliant - they really [blank] I had in mind when I was writing it.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "drawings" }, { "answer": "create the atmosphere" }],
        "translation": "是的，我看了你给我故事那些森林画的手绘，真的很赞！它们营造出了我写作时构想的那种氛围。"
