        "text": "I've seen a list of plays that are being performed this week, and I'd like to know which are [blank] my children, and which ones my husband and I might go to.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "suitable for" }],
        "translation": "我看了一下这周的表演名单，我想问一下哪些适合我的孩子们，哪些适合我和我的先生？"
