        "text": "Well, if you want a [blank] done what I'd need to do is strip the old paint and plaster it about a week before I paint it. Of course.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "proper job" }],
        "translation": "那么，如果你想让活计完成的漂亮，我需要把原先的油漆去掉，然后在我刷漆之前大概一周给这片墙刷一遍石膏。当然。"
