        "text": "It's easy enough to do, because there's a [blank] called STEP - S- T- E- P - that [blank] placements for students.",
        "blanks": [{ "answer": "government agency" }, { "answer": "organises" }],
        "translation": "其实很简单，因为有个叫做“STEP”S-T-E-P的政府机构为学生组织实习。"
