        "speaker": "Speaker",
        "text": "The problem with this is that women can be tall and still have much [blank] shoulders than the average man. Ill- fitting PPE such as hi- vis jackets, vests and body armour can put women at risk. The report found that [blank] said that their PPE often hampered their work and that this problem was worst in the [blank], particularly the police.",
